    <p>Dr. Dean Ornish is a pioneer of lifestyle medicine who proved, for the first time, that heart disease can be reversed through intensive lifestyle changes alone - without drugs or surgery. His landmark research in the 1990s showed actual regression of coronary atherosclerosis in patients who followed his program.</p>

